title: !!1 Month FREE!! Top floor 1BR apt, City views, Fully-equipped kitchen
posting_body: ['The Elliott Pointe Apartments offers unique studio, one and two bedroom floor plans to suit your desire for luxury apartment living.', 'Our apartments feature fantastic designer-colored walls, luxury plank floor, and stainless steel kitchen appliances.', 'This apartment features:', 'Top floor with city views', 'Incredible Elliott Bay and skyline views!', 'Fully-equipped, stainless kitchen', 'Desired open concept kitchen has breakfast bar', 'Cozy fireplace', 'Stainless steel kitchen appliances', 'Generous Storage', 'Full-size washer/dryer in laundry room!', 'Come Visit us!', 'Elliott Pointe', '2226 Elliott Avenue', 'Seattle, WA 98121', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours -- Come visit us during our office hours for more information and tours!', 'Monday – Friday', '9:00am – 6:00pm', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: Elliott Bay, Pike Place Market, Seattle Waterfront, Bell Street Bridge, Belltown, Seattle Art Institute, highway 5, highway 99, Pier 66']
